Sure, their troops lack combat experience.

233
00:11:36,980 --> 00:11:38,670
But some of their weapons could still cause

234
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:41,490
major damage to the US in a war.

235
00:11:41,490 --> 00:11:44,610
And the Chinese Communist Party televised
the whole parade,

236
